Print statistics about all Rust projects in the directory

Usage: stats [OPTIONS]

Options:
  -d, --dry-run
          Run the program without making any changes

  -p, --path <PATH>
          Path to a directory

  -e, --exclude <EXCLUDE>
          Exclude the provided folder from the size calculation and cleaning default is `None` - you can specify multiple folders separated by `,`

  -h, --help
          Print help

  -V, --version
          Print version
